      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流配送路线系统的Git流程图，重点是展示从main分支合并到未开发分支的过程。标题就叫\"Merge from main onto undeveloped branch (Logistics_DeliveryRoute)\"吧。",
