    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，方向用LR横向布局对吗？还有您说的\"undeveloped branch\"，我在图里是用develop分支来代表，还是直接叫undeveloped？",
      "elements_involved": [
