    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，横向布局。分支名用develop就行，代表开发中的功能分支。流程是：先有个初始commit，然后切出develop分支做开发，同时main分支继续往前走，最后把main的新内容合并回develop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "develop",
        "main",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：初始commit，然后branch develop，develop上再commit。接着checkout回main继续commit，再切回develop执行merge main。这样develop就包含了main的最新更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout main",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，develop上只有一个commit吗？我需要确认下——develop分支切出来后，是不是应该先有个提交，然后再去处理main的合并？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，develop切出后有一个commit，然后checkout main再commit，这时候main和develop是并行的。最后checkout develop把main合并进来，形成完整的合并历史。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "checkout",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以，这样逻辑就清晰了。不过标题里的\"undeveloped\"可能有点歧义，要不要改成\"development\"？算了，保持原样吧，强调的是合并到未完全开发的分支这个场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "undeveloped",
